trans-unit.source: Specifies a palette when setting a Palette property.
trans-unit.target: Especifica uma paleta quando definir uma propriedade de paleta.

trans-unit.source: The ChartColorPalette enumeration represents the palettes to be used for the root <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> object and any <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> objects.
trans-unit.target: A enumeração de ChartColorPalette representa palettes a ser utilizada para a raiz <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>objeto e quaisquer <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>objetos.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If no colors are assigned to data points and their associated series, the default colors will be assigned to the data.
trans-unit.target: Se nenhum cores forem atribuídas aos pontos de dados e as séries associadas, as cores predefinida serão atribuídas aos dados.

trans-unit.source: For example: - If <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A> is set to None, then the default palette is set to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.PaletteCustomColors%2A> or BrightPastel.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo: - se <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A>está definida como None, em seguida, a paleta de predefinição está definida como <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.PaletteCustomColors%2A>ou BrightPastel.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.PaletteCustomColors%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A>

trans-unit.source: If.<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.Palette%2A> is set to None, then the default palette for the chart is used (<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Se. <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.Palette%2A>está definida como None, a paleta de predefinido para o gráfico será utilizado (<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Palette%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.Palette%2A>
Utiliza a paleta de cores bright.
Utiliza a paleta de cores pastel bright.

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes earth tone colors such as green and brown.
trans-unit.target: Utiliza a paleta de cores earth tone como verde e castanha.
Utiliza a paleta de cores de estilo de Excel.

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes red, orange and yellow colors.
trans-unit.target: Utiliza a paleta de cores vermelha, laranja e amarela.

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes grayscale colors, that is, shades of black and white.
trans-unit.target: Paleta utiliza em tons de cinzento cores, ou seja, shades de negra e branco.

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LightStyle"></xref> style colors; very light colors..
trans-unit.target: Utiliza a paleta <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LightStyle"> </xref> cores de estilo; cores muito ligeira...
Utiliza a paleta de cores pastel.

trans-unit.source: Palette utilizes colors that range from green to blue.
trans-unit.target: Paleta utiliza cores que variam entre verde para azul.
Utiliza a paleta de cores por transparentes.
